txt.en: Dagrun can be found in the Trade Commission Headquarters.\n\nYou should talk to Dagrun.
The Lake-town Smugglers are notorious for their black market trading. Dagrun has asked you to destroy any ill-gotten goods you find while inside the smugglers' hideout.
Smuggled goods can be found inside the smugglers' hideout in Lake-town.\n\nYou should destroy smuggled goods.

'While you're cleaning out the smugglers, would you mind cleaning out their ill-gotten goods as well? We've found enough evidence to lock Sk√≥tmun away for good, and I don't want any questionable items resurfacing because we failed to take care of it right away! Just go ahead and destroy any you find.'
'You destroyed how much?! Thank you for taking care of that, [placeholder]. Now none of it will make it out onto the streets.'
